Repository: base
Title: PPPoE (PPP over Ethernet) common
Maintainer: Daniel Dickinson <lede@cshore.thecshore.com>
Source: rp-pppoe-3.12.tar.gz
License: LGPL-2.0+
Type: ipkg
Description:   Dubbed RP-PPPoE, this open-source product is ideal for Linux users with
  a DSL "modem" whose Internet service provider uses PPPoE.

 This package contains files common to server and relay.
http://roaringpenguin.com/products/pppoe
Daniel Dickinson <lede@cshore.thecshore.com>
@@

